==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Plasterer
<hw>Plas"ter*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who applies plaster or mortar.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Thy father was a
<xex>plasterer</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who makes plaster casts.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>plasterer</xex> doth make his figures by addition.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Sir H. Wotton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plastering</ent>⟦br⟧
